      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 high-compression inline-six. This example boasts a linear power band optimized by individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to address chassis fatigue common in the platform. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, retaining its factory-spec suspension geometry and original aerodynamic efficiency. A turn-key investment for the purist seeking an unmolested, atmospheric masterpiece.",
